item.description:
ONLY OFFICIAL Latina Women Party for us and all of our amigas/os of color!

Viernes Social for Amigas begins at 9 p.m. At Frans Place in Lynn. Special suprises, giveaways and so much more! A Fun Viernes Social with pool tables, dancing, amigas, and great music! Proper ID Required. THE ONLY OFFICIAL EVENT FOR WOMEN & OUR FRIENDS, don't be going to the wrong party - this is the party to go! Announcing a special performance from JenRo, the hiphop national artist! Come and enjoy a night of Amigas, great music and JenRo! You won't want to miss this special night! $7, tickets to be sold at the door!

More info at Somos Latin@s.

(Note: We are helping our friends at Somos Latin@s promote this event.)
